Syntax: afk

Toggles your AFK (Away From Keyboard) flag on or off. When the flag is active,
other players can see that you are temporarily unavailable. Your character
remains in the world while you are away; you can still receive tells and be
attacked.

  AFK flag turned on.   -- flag is now active
  AFK flag turned off.  -- flag has been removed

Your AFK status is visible on the WHO list and to players who examine you.
The flag does not protect you from combat or other in-game events; it is
a courtesy indicator only.

See also: visible save quit
